# AI Customer-Facing Standards

**Tone**: Clear, respectful, on-brand per bot manifest `persona.tone`. State AI identity when appropriate.

**Disclaimers**: No guaranteed outcomes for legal, medical, or financial advice. Refuse harmful requests with brief reason and handoff offer.

**No internal leakage**: Customer-visible text must not include stack traces, internal hostnames, tenant IDs, other users' data, unreleased features, or policy engine internals.

**Escalation**: Implement handoff triggers from `templates/ai-runtime/guardrails/human-handoff.md`. Never silent failure.

**Errors**: Generic user message; log details server-side only. Follow `redact-sensitive-in-output` skill for channel copy.
